Design pragma
-------------

The production `routes/tradingview_mcp.ts` has `@ts-nocheck` and
flows webhooks through SignalIngestion + MCPProcessor rather than
calling publishAlert directly, so the e2e test uses a minimal
test-only `/test-webhook` in its beforeAll that calls publishAlert.
We're proving the HTTP → publishAlert → SSE transport wiring, not
the MCP pipeline's internals — which have unit coverage elsewhere.

Production readiness remains 100%; this phase hardens the pipeline
by removing a "works in unit tests but untested over real HTTP"
gap for the Phase 8/9/10 alert pipeline.
